# Incident Report – Case 01: HR Onboarding Phishing Email (False Positive)

## Time of Activity
05/25/2026 02:30:35.320

---

## Summary
An inbound email was flagged due to an external onboarding link from a third-party HR domain. Investigation included email correlation and historical communication review to validate legitimacy.

---

## Affected Entities
- Sender: onboarding@hrconnex.thm
- Recipient: j.garcia@thetrydaily.thm
- Domain: hrconnex.thm
- URL: https://hrconnex.thm/onboarding/15400654060/j.garcia
- Source IP (web access): 10.20.2.17 / 67.199.248.11

---

## Investigation Steps
- Checked SIEM email logs for related communication
- Correlated internal HR onboarding threads
- Reviewed firewall logs for URL access attempts
- Checked threat intelligence reputation for domain and URL

---

## Key Findings
- Internal email confirmed HR onboarding process reference
- No malicious execution or endpoint compromise
- URL categorized as low risk in threat intelligence (1/92 detection)
- Firewall blocked outbound access attempt

---

## Conclusion
False Positive – legitimate onboarding workflow with external HR provider

---

## Escalation Decision
No escalation required

---

## Remediation Actions
- No isolation required
- Continue monitoring for phishing patterns
- User awareness recommended for external onboarding links

